Package: clash-config-gen
Version: 1.0.0-1
Depends: libc, coreutils-base64
Source: https://github.com/albawid/ClashConfigGen
Section: net
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Albawid <albawid@users.noreply.github.com>
Description: Clash Config Generator for OpenWrt - Convert VMess/VLESS/SS/Trojan URIs to OpenClash YAML
  Converts proxy URIs (vmess://, vless://, ss://, trojan://) to 
  OpenClash compatible YAML config. Output is terminal-friendly 
  for easy copy-paste to OpenClash configuration.
